{"tid":1957210,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(正視聽) 熊茶被批鬥 只係因為行為不當 而唔係因為黃藍問題","createTime":"2020-04-03T17:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T01:09:01.000Z","uid":100227,"like":41,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2dd30760c0767c0ff38c9fbd29f2dcbcf2ff02","tid":1957210,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:35:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Thumb Rule: 黃色經濟圈嘅概念自身係無錯</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n熊茶呢次只係個別黃店作出行為不當事件 <br />\n而黃色經濟圈嘅概念係無錯嘅 錯嘅係利用呢樣嘢去賺錢嘅人<br />\n支持黃色經濟圈嘅大家 無做錯任何嘢<br />\n五毛就係想帶風向 <br />\n等大家因為一兩次呢啲事件而對黃色經濟圈呢個概念有懷疑<br />\n從而用內鬥 失敗論 令大家心淡 自行解散黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請唔好覺得氣餒 錯嘅只係利用黃色經濟圈嘅人</span></strong>"},{"pid":"28e016645398040cc31f4c03e70f4455a8f36926","tid":1957210,"uid":35693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次只係個別事件！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"460a596f604c58759fd003a2660fc94d05461f25","tid":1957210,"uid":100227,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"28e016645398040cc31f4c03e70f4455a8f36926","tid":1957210,"uid":35693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次只係個別事件！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"無錯 嚟嚟去去 咪都係得串燒保 同 熊茶 兩間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樹大有枯枝 只係個別事件 <br />\n人哋利用黃色經濟圈掠水 我哋阻止唔到<br />\n今次比人利用告急 大家發現咗之後 <br />\n去葵廣咪唔好幫襯熊茶 幫襯第二間黃飲品店囉<br />\n黃店有千千萬萬 一單半單呢啲個別事件一定有<br />\n唔好比五毛帶風向"},{"pid":"b48a1b385e6b581ecf6cb25410008a1d5b91e1c4","tid":1957210,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bb555436f7524ad1cdea512168989bf0a2b96b","tid":1957210,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"「解悶工廠」 點解還押抗爭者仲睇到連登？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1956428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1956428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c53f6549f5b4e084b782a7d63d1401f69c18874","tid":1957210,"uid":150483,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:00:27.000Z","msg":"A :咁d黃店屎咁難食係咪都含淚食<br />\nB :黃店做乜都要擁護<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">AB 利申 我好黃架</span>"},{"pid":"d0a79cf74cee32d4fdd19b5e2b02451b5f5d2fe2","tid":1957210,"uid":100227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「 黃藍是政見 黑白是良知」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得呢句說話?<br />\n<br />\n1. 黃+白 = 優先幫襯<br />\n2. 黃+黑 = 唔幫襯 (<del>藍+白</del> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 藍同白根本mutually exclusive)<br />\n3. 藍+黑 = 一世唔好幫襯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>分黃藍店嘅同時 仲要分清黑白店!</strong></span>"},{"pid":"fdac1ef1c882a05c95c68b1597d116263932c801","tid":1957210,"uid":100227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c53f6549f5b4e084b782a7d63d1401f69c18874","tid":1957210,"uid":150483,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:00:27.000Z","msg":"A :咁d黃店屎咁難食係咪都含淚食<br />\nB :黃店做乜都要擁護<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">AB 利申 我好黃架</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:03:24.000Z","msg":"黃藍只係基本要求 <br />\n大家都要認清黑白是非"},{"pid":"5f79490ef681cb9f104c6d04818cc2c5ad190588","tid":1957210,"uid":35693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c53f6549f5b4e084b782a7d63d1401f69c18874","tid":1957210,"uid":150483,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:00:27.000Z","msg":"A :咁d黃店屎咁難食係咪都含淚食<br />\nB :黃店做乜都要擁護<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">AB 利申 我好黃架</span>"},"citedBy":0,"reply